<li><a href="http://www.fda.gov/ohrms/dockets/ac/01/transcripts/3750t1_01.pdf" rel="nofollow">Transcript of FDA meeting, in which, starting page 77, Dr. Alex Van der Eb describes in detail the origin of HEK 293 cell</a> .pdf</li>
</ul>
